# Supabase Integration

This project uses Supabase for authentication, database, and storage. The integration is organized as follows:

## Key Files
- [lib/supabase/client.ts](mdc:lib/supabase/client.ts) - Browser client for client-side components
- [lib/supabase/server.ts](mdc:lib/supabase/server.ts) - Server client for server components
- [lib/supabase/middleware.ts](mdc:lib/supabase/middleware.ts) - Middleware integration for auth
- [lib/supabase/forms.ts](mdc:lib/supabase/forms.ts) - Form-specific Supabase functions
- [lib/supabase/types.ts](mdc:lib/supabase/types.ts) - TypeScript definitions for database tables

## Database Schema
The database includes tables for:
- `forms` - Form definitions
- `form_fields` - Fields within forms
- `form_responses` - User submissions
- `roles` - User roles
- `permissions` - Available permissions
- `roles_permissions` - Join table for roles and permissions
